{"id": 57927, "date": "2025-08-07T04:00:05", "date_gmt": "2025-08-07T11:00:05", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57927"}, "modified": "2026-05-12T14:52:52", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-12T21:52:52", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-7-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/07/kingdom-of-days-august-7-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 7"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band headlines at Asbury Park&#8217;s Sunshine In.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20202\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-08-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?fit=2077%2C1497&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2077,1497\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-08-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?fit=758%2C546&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20202 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?resize=758%2C546&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"546\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?w=2077&amp;ssl=1 2077w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?resize=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?resize=1024%2C738&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?resize=768%2C554&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?resize=1536%2C1107&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1971-08-07.png?resize=2048%2C1476&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3519\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-0807/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1971-0807.jpg?fit=493%2C640&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"493,640\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;P 25&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1115822458&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-0807\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1971-0807.jpg?fit=493%2C640&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3519 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1971-0807.jpg?resize=493%2C640&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"493\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1971-0807.jpg?w=493&amp;ssl=1 493w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1971-0807.jpg?resize=231%2C300&amp;ssl=1 231w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973: </strong>A scheduled show at Uncle Al&#8217;s Erlton Theatre Lounge in Cherry Hill is likely postponed (no record exists of this show having taken place) to the following week. Instead, Bruce works on overdubs and mixing for &#8220;Thundercrack,&#8221; &#8220;New York City Serenade,&#8221; and &#8220;Zero and Blind Terry.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"53969\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/courier_post_1973_07_21_page_25/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?fit=1832%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1832,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?fit=733%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-53969 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C1059&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1059\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?w=1832&amp;ssl=1 1832w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?resize=215%2C300&amp;ssl=1 215w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?resize=733%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 733w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1073&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Courier_Post_1973_07_21_Page_25-scaled.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up their six-night stand at the Monmouth Arts Center in Red Bank, New Jersey. Clips from the show can be seen in the box set and documentary, <em>The Promise: The Making of Darkness on the Edge of Town</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ioQ2eF1XbYY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3527\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-0807/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1976-0807.jpg?fit=499%2C553&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"499,553\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1431182019&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-0807\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1976-0807.jpg?fit=499%2C553&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3527 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1976-0807.jpg?resize=499%2C553&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"553\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1976-0807.jpg?w=499&amp;ssl=1 499w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1976-0807.jpg?resize=271%2C300&amp;ssl=1 271w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>The Darkness Tour stop in Kalamazoo underperforms in ticket sales, with over half of the seats at Wings Stadium going unoccupied.</p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up their three-night stand at the Capital Center in Largo, Maryland.</p>\n<div id=\"v-0KQVFFpL-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/0KQVFFpL?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Beaver Brown on stage at Big Man&#8217;s West in Red Bank, where he debuts a work-in-progress, &#8220;Downbound Train&#8221; in the middle of &#8220;Lucille.&#8221; (Skip to the 21 minute-mark below to hear it.)</p>\n<div id=\"v-9dFjGaHk-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/9dFjGaHk?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28557\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1982-08-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?fit=615%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"615,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1982-08-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?fit=246%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28557 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?resize=615%2C2560&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"615\" height=\"2560\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?w=615&amp;ssl=1 615w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?resize=72%2C300&amp;ssl=1 72w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?resize=246%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 246w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?resize=369%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 369w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1982-08-07-scaled.jpg?resize=492%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 492w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 615px) 100vw, 615px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong><em>Born in the U.S.A.\u00a0</em>is certified platinum by the Recording Industry Association of America.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_knulz6rBDTjgdDwskLxzD8g7gAdqRY4T0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>The stadium leg of the Born in the U.S.A. Tour picks up steam at Cleveland Municipal Stadium, where Bruce tour debuts &#8220;This Land is Your Land.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-Vu6tENsx-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Vu6tENsx?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20203\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-08-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1985-08-07.png?fit=1860%2C1634&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1860,1634\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;cre