jpg?resize=758%2C691&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"691\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1985-0807.jpg?w=798&amp;ssl=1 798w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1985-0807.jpg?resize=300%2C273&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1985-0807.jpg?resize=768%2C700&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>At the penultimate show of World Tour 1992&#8217;s eleven-night stand at the Meadowlands, Bruce and Roy play a tour one-off, an intimate &#8220;For You.&#8221; &#8220;Racing in the Street&#8221; is also a tour one-off, and Southside Johnny guest-stars on &#8220;All the Way Home.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-MZxl9BXf-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/MZxl9BXf?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-iGI2fvg3-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/iGI2fvg3?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-Xl1kGK8C-1\" class=\"video-player\"><